data.description: LOW Tipton County taxes! Stunning 5BR/3BA custom built home on over 3 acres w/1 acre fenced. They pulled out all the stops on this one: 8ft doors throughout, Energy Star Certified, oversized garage, convection oven & microwave, black stainless steel appliance, 6-burner gas stove, 3-zone HVAC, new deck, fiber cable & surround sound, 1200 sqft unfinished to make your own, the best pantry. All this for a 2.5% VA assumable or seller is offering $5000 to buy down your interest rate w/accept offer.
